556
00:43:12,045 --> 00:43:13,079
I see.

557
00:43:14,362 --> 00:43:19,484
I'm shocked that Woosik lasted
so long with your temper.

558
00:43:20,928 --> 00:43:22,663
That's enough.

559
00:43:22,989 --> 00:43:26,542
Drop me off at the terminal and go home.

560
00:43:26,645 --> 00:43:28,248
How many times will you say that?

561
00:43:28,359 --> 00:43:30,247
I said it twice. Only twice.

562
00:43:36,837 --> 00:43:37,900
It'll be okay.

563
00:43:38,705 --> 00:43:41,106
I survived even after my husband died.

564
00:43:43,910 --> 00:43:46,608
Drop me off at the terminal...

565
00:43:46,719 --> 00:43:47,781
I know.

566
00:43:47,895 --> 00:43:50,322
I'll drop you off and go home.

567
00:44:17,889 --> 00:44:19,193
Help me.

568
00:44:23,884 --> 00:44:25,257
Please help me!

569
00:44:25,485 --> 00:44:27,134
Please!

570
00:44:29,952 --> 00:44:33,756
Please take me away from here.

571
00:44:33,902 --> 00:44:34,903
Mom.

572
00:44:35,005 --> 00:44:36,707
Are you crazy?

573
