578
00:44:54,400 --> 00:44:55,675
I'm so tired.

579
00:44:55,982 --> 00:44:57,778
But you can't stop the champion.

580
00:44:57,918 --> 00:45:00,772
Okay. I'll train Junseong.

581
00:45:00,874 --> 00:45:01,770
You should get some rest.

582
00:45:04,105 --> 00:45:05,129
Yes, sir.

583
00:45:05,392 --> 00:45:07,704
Thank you. I love you.

584
00:45:16,815 --> 00:45:17,816
Is he here already?

585
00:45:47,878 --> 00:45:48,879
Goodness.

586
00:45:50,470 --> 00:45:51,771
What are you doing?

587
00:45:54,641 --> 00:45:55,642
John Kim said...

588
00:45:55,756 --> 00:45:57,278
Who cares about what John Kim said?

589
00:45:59,846 --> 00:46:01,948
What do you mean, "who cares"?

590
00:46:02,115 --> 00:46:04,768
Do you really think
this will make you lose weight?

591
00:46:04,964 --> 00:46:05,842
If you do,

592
00:46:06,500 --> 00:46:07,901
what would change?

593
00:46:08,288 --> 00:46:11,332
Why are you so serious?
I'm just trying to lose weight.

594
00:46:12,989 --> 00:46:14,135
I was told,

595
00:46:15,196 --> 00:46:17,198
to do as much as I could,

596
00:46:17,791 --> 00:46:20,060
so that's what I intend to do.

597
00:46:24,552 --> 00:46:26,454
You've already exceeded your limit.

598
00:46:28,642 --> 00:46:29,643
I did not.

599
00:46:30,577 --> 00:46:31,778
I can do anything...

600
00:46:32,212 --> 00:46:34,383
...if I put my mind to it.

601
00:46:35,515 --> 00:46:37,126
I can still do it.

602
00:46:37,951 --> 00:46:39,728
That means I haven't reached my limit yet.

603
00:46:40,415 --> 00:46:41,816
Believing that you can do something...

604
00:46:42,022 --> 00:46:43,950
....is different from being able to do it.

605
00:46:44,825 --> 00:46:46,179
It's the same to me.

606
00:46:48,395 --> 00:46:49,996
If I believe it, I can do it.

607
00:46:50,709 --> 00:46:52,378
I believe that I can.

608
00:46:54,914 --> 00:46:56,411
If I do one more repetition,

609
00:46:57,357 --> 00:46:58,859
it'll be 107 times.

610
00:46:59,706 --> 00:47:00,998
Lucky seven.

611
00:47:03,893 --> 00:47:04,995
You need to stop.

612
00:47:05,846 --> 00:47:07,778
I can do it. Let go.

613
00:47:07,981 --> 00:47:09,209
Listen to me.

614
00:47:10,750 --> 00:47:12,016
You might hurt yourself.

615
00:47:17,554 --> 00:47:20,256
You didn't need to call a driver.

616
00:47:21,094 --> 00:47:23,125
It's the same price as taking the taxi.

617
00:47:25,086 --> 00:47:27,729
You may be unable to control your body.

618
00:47:28,001 --> 00:47:30,047
You need to think of the safety of others.

619
00:47:32,017 --> 00:47:33,142
Did you ask for a driver?

620
00:47:33,429 --> 00:47:34,430
Yes.

621
00:47:36,431 --> 00:47:37,432
Please take her home.

622
00:47:37,719 --> 00:47:38,442
Yes, sir.

623
00:47:40,647 --> 00:47:42,849
Okay, then. Bye.

624
00:47:55,896 --> 00:47:57,467
Don't think about anything.

625
00:47:57,586 --> 00:48:00,000
Take a warm shower before going to bed.

626
00:48:00,161 --> 00:48:02,556
Then, you'll feel better tomorrow.

627
00:48:15,715 --> 00:48:17,349
Isn't that Lawyer Kang's car?

628
00:48:18,648 --> 00:48:19,452
Yes.

629
