630
00:48:23,848 --> 00:48:25,498
She's really trying hard.

631
00:48:25,754 --> 00:48:30,091
She's ignorant, brave
and determined, too.

632
00:48:32,984 --> 00:48:34,063
Don't get off.

633
00:48:34,880 --> 00:48:36,748
Let's rest tonight.

634
00:48:37,193 --> 00:48:37,908
