"Are you sure
you want to delete this contact?"

640
00:49:26,876 --> 00:49:29,660
"Contact deleted"

641
00:49:30,351 --> 00:49:34,359
"Trainer JK"

642
00:49:40,844 --> 00:49:42,114
John Kim.

643
00:49:42,563 --> 00:49:45,355
I'll work harder tomorrow.

644
00:49:45,902 --> 00:49:49,160
Please believe that
I really want to do this.

645
00:49:51,772 --> 00:49:53,307
I'll see you tomorrow.

646
00:49:54,862 --> 00:49:55,961
But...

647
00:49:56,644 --> 00:49:57,811
...can...

648
00:49:58,612 --> 00:49:59,710
...I...

649
00:50:00,868 --> 00:50:03,786
...really change?

650
00:50:11,537 --> 00:50:12,756
Believing that you can do something...

651
00:50:12,865 --> 00:50:14,563
...is different from being able to do it.

652
00:50:14,664 --> 00:50:15,985
It's the same to me.

653
00:50:18,252 --> 00:50:19,787
If I believe it, I can do it.

654
00:50:20,570 --> 00:50:22,203
I believe that I can.

655
00:50:25,343 --> 00:50:26,811
