662
00:51:17,569 --> 00:51:19,691
...and they want a female attorney.

663
00:51:21,875 --> 00:51:25,260
Am I the only female attorney at our firm?

664
00:51:25,366 --> 00:51:28,859
There are four.
You, me, Lawyer Kim and Lawyer Choi.

665
00:51:29,444 --> 00:51:31,334
I have an important meeting
this afternoon,

666
00:51:31,437 --> 00:51:33,010
and Lawyer Kim is in court.

667
00:51:33,278 --> 00:51:35,170
Lawyer Choi has stage fright.

668
00:51:36,777 --> 00:51:38,468
You must have forgotten.

669
00:51:38,590 --> 00:51:40,794
I have everything the others have.

670
00:51:42,878 --> 00:51:44,546
I'm getting nauseous.

671
00:51:46,189 --> 00:51:48,540
The president is happy because
it'll be good publicity.

672
00:51:48,642 --> 00:51:50,072
Don't disappoint him.

673
00:51:50,934 --> 00:51:52,068
Hey, Soojin.

674
00:51:54,028 --> 00:51:55,663
Are you trying to get revenge?

675
