Why?

676
00:51:57,798 --> 00:51:59,154
Why are you doing this?

677
00:52:00,137 --> 00:52:01,147
Revenge?

678
00:52:02,316 --> 00:52:06,022
Why is asking you to go on TV, a revenge?

679
00:52:18,615 --> 00:52:22,643
For example, using a photo from
someone else's SNS...

680
00:52:31,659 --> 00:52:32,688
That's bitter.

681
00:52:35,302 --> 00:52:38,204
You have lots of guts, Jooeun.

682
00:52:38,572 --> 00:52:39,679
This is nothing.

683
00:52:39,868 --> 00:52:40,938
Get yourself together.

684
00:52:43,844 --> 00:52:44,985
That scared me.

685
00:52:45,112 --> 00:52:46,447
Gosh.

686
00:52:49,471 --> 00:52:54,082
Article 46 of the Copyright Law states...

687
00:52:56,745 --> 00:52:58,708
What's wrong with my voice?

688
00:53:05,900 --> 00:53:07,200
John Kim.

689
00:53:07,599 --> 00:53:10,201
I have to appear on TV this afternoon.

690
00:53:10,723 --> 00:53:14,160
I'm reporting that I'll have
to skip my afternoon run.

691
00:53:14,786 --> 00:53:17,017
I'm nervous, but I'll do my best.

692
00:53:18,468 --> 00:53:20,897
"My Ma'am"

693
00:53:21,095 --> 00:53:22,618
Is she there already?

694
00:53:26,607 --> 00:53:28,216
She can't make it.

695
00:53:30,152 --> 00:53:31,104
Good luck!

696
00:53:35,062 --> 00:53:36,553
What luck?

697
00:53:37,396 --> 00:53:41,067
Today we will be discussing
copyright infringement...

698
00:53:41,192 --> 00:53:44,178
...that can be committed easily
without realizing it.

699
00:53:44,765 --> 00:53:46,486
I taught Jooeun how to...

700
00:53:47,489 --> 00:53:49,118
"Mother-in-law"

701
00:53:52,166 --> 00:53:53,356
Are you trying to get revenge?

702
00:53:53,471 --> 00:53:56,040
Why is asking you to go on TV, a revenge?

703
00:53:56,171 --> 00:54:00,308
We have Lawyer Kang Jooeun with us today.

704
00:54:00,575 --> 00:54:01,471
Hello.

705
00:54:01,809 --> 00:54:04,177
Hello, I'm Attorney Kang Jooeun.

706
00:54:04,307 --> 00:54:06,880
What's wrong with her face?

707
00:54:07,882 --> 00:54:10,523
Article 46 of the Copyright Law states,

708
00:54:10,718 --> 00:54:13,834
that if you wish to use
someone else's creative work,

709
00:54:14,023 --> 00:54:16,947
you must obtain their consent,

710
00:54:17,091 --> 00:54:19,295
regardless of whether or not
you use it for profit.

711
00:54:20,682 --> 00:54:22,787
Most importantly, one should keep in mind,

712
00:54:22,997 --> 00:54:27,402
that it is the same as stealing
someone's money or property.

713
00:54:27,517 --> 00:54:31,195
One should be aware of this
and act morally.

714
00:54:31,539 --> 00:54:32,640
I see.

715
00:54:32,774 --> 00:54:35,276
Thank you for your time.

716
00:54:41,043 --> 00:54:44,566
We had a slight accident
during our live broadcast.

717
00:54:44,686 --> 00:54:48,289
We ask for your understanding.

718
00:54:54,557 --> 00:54:56,084
We'll go for commercials.

719
00:54:59,677 --> 00:55:01,879
-Lawyer Kang.
-Call an ambulance.

720
00:55:02,003 --> 00:55:03,304
-Hurry.
-Lawyer Kang.

721
00:55:03,396 --> 00:55:04,396
Lawyer Kang.

722
00:55:07,842 --> 00:55:09,855
It's the second time
I've been in an ambulance.

723
00:55:10,345 --> 00:55:12,656
Where am I going?

724
00:55:14,194 --> 00:55:15,408
The first time,

725
00:55:15,717 --> 00:55:17,886
they took off my corset.

726
00:55:18,620 --> 00:55:21,178
What will happen to me this time?

727
00:55:35,450 --> 00:55:36,368
Oh, no.

728
00:55:39,574 --> 00:55:40,919
Woosik, it's me.

729
00:55:41,020 --> 00:55:43,761
-Jooeun...
-Sorry. I'll call you back later.

730
00:55:45,064 --> 00:55:47,064
Where are you going?

731
00:55:47,549 --> 00:55:48,886
I'll call you when I'm back.

732
00:56:50,411 --> 00:56:51,527
How did you know?

733
00:56:53,078 --> 00:56:55,956
I was nearby.

734
00:56:57,003 --> 00:56:58,042
I see.

735
00:57:07,061 --> 00:57:08,759
