who ripped it off this time.

736
00:57:18,781 --> 00:57:20,011
How do you feel?

737
00:57:21,356 --> 00:57:23,745
You have a new worst day of your life.

738
00:57:25,580 --> 00:57:27,417
I've been better.

739
00:57:27,592 --> 00:57:29,513
That's for sure.

740
00:57:31,419 --> 00:57:33,597
