interested in me...

744
00:57:44,866 --> 00:57:46,516
You never know.

745
00:57:47,069 --> 00:57:48,498
And let's not be rude.

746
00:58:04,700 --> 00:58:06,806
I'm grateful,

747
00:58:07,683 --> 00:58:09,843
