a chance to thank you.

748
00:58:10,491 --> 00:58:14,696
Anyway, I keep owing you.

749
00:58:18,760 --> 00:58:19,881
Thank you.

750
00:58:20,198 --> 00:58:21,317
Goodbye.

751
00:58:37,295 --> 00:58:39,287
