let's do it right.

752
00:58:42,265 --> 00:58:43,116
I am...

753
00:58:43,858 --> 00:58:44,966
...John Kim.

754
00:59:13,863 --> 00:59:15,950
"Oh My Venus"

755
00:59:16,053 --> 00:59:19,448
Do you have proof that
you are in fact, John Kim?

756
00:59:19,609 --> 00:59:20,558
Get lost!

757
00:59:20,678 --> 00:59:22,213
This evil witch.

758
00:59:22,326 --> 00:59:23,694
That swollen face.

759
00:59:23,852 --> 00:59:25,257
It's all over.

760
00:59:25,363 --> 00:59:27,860
I went to see Jooeun.
She had someone there.

761
00:59:27,999 --> 00:59:29,344
Why are you here so early?

762
00:59:29,471 --> 00:59:31,018
Do you have a boyfriend?

763
00:59:31,110 --> 00:59:32,945
-She was dumped.
-Oh, my gosh.

764
00:59:34,756 --> 00:59:37,741
Sleeping, walking, eating, and moving.

765
00:59:37,875 --> 00:59:40,378
You must redo them all. Okay?

766
00:59:41,676 --> 00:59:43,481
Jooeun, it's me.

767
00:59:48,186 --> 00:59:49,430
Help me.
